OL,3,CCouncil accused of treating residents
OL,4,Cin 'shameful manner' over Aqua Park
OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,FA Welsh council has been urged to
OL,8,Fexplain itself after an email trail
OL,9,Fwas published showing talks between it
OL,10,Fand a leisure company over plans for a
OL,11,Fcontroversial water park.
OL,13,FThe Save Cosmeston and the Vale
OL,14,Fcampaign group, which is opposed to
OL,15,Fthe opening of a new Aqua Park site at
OL,16,FCosmeston Lakes, obtained the email
OL,17,Ftrail between Vale of Glamorgan
OL,18,FCouncil and Aqua Park Group via a
OL,19,Ffreedom of information request.
