OL,7,FIn the correspondence between a
OL,8,Fcouncil officer and Aqua Park earlier
OL,9,Fthis year the company proposed
OL,10,Fdiscussing a potential 15-year term
OL,11,Ffor the site and was told that there
OL,12,Fwas "agreement to move forward with
OL,13,Fyou behind the scenes".
