OL,7,FVale of Glamorgan Council's leader,
OL,8,FCllr Lis Burnett, has responded saying
OL,9,Fno agreement to begin the trial of the
OL,10,FAqua Park attraction was made before
OL,11,Fthe decision by cabinet members in
OL,12,FMarch 2025 and that the 15-year
OL,13,Fproposal was the company's suggestion
OL,14,Falone.
OL,16,FA council spokesman also said that
OL,17,F"moving forward" refers to moving
OL,18,Fforward with the preparation of a
OL,19,Fdraft heads of terms document and
OL,20,Fdiscussions on requirements for water
OL,21,Fsampling and other operational issues.
