OL,7,FPlans to trial an Aqua Park attraction
OL,8,Fat the eastern side of Cosmeston Lakes
OL,9,Fwere discussed publicly at a cabinet
OL,10,Fmeeting in March 2025 and looked at by
OL,11,Fan environmental scrutiny committee
OL,12,Fbefore a licence agreement was signed
OL,13,Fin April.
OL,15,FHowever discussions about this
OL,16,Fparticular scheme go back as far as
OL,17,FJanuary 2025 and a number of
OL,18,Fcouncillors have criticised the local
OL,19,Fauthority of not involving locally-
OL,20,Felected representatives and residents
OL,21,Fsooner.
