OL,7,FConservative ward councillor for
OL,8,FPlymouth, Cllr Anothony Ernest, said
OL,9,Fthe scheme had been "very badly
OL,10,Fhandled" and Plaid Cymru group leader
OL,11,FCllr Ian Johnson said he had "strong
OL,12,Fconcerns" about how quickly it went
OL,13,Ffrom being publicised to getting
OL,14,Fapproval.
