OL,7,FAnother Conservative councillor, also
OL,8,Frepresenting the Plymouth ward which
OL,9,FCosmeston Lakes is situated in, Cllr
OL,10,FRhys Thomas, said: "A full and fair
OL,11,Fconsultation should have happened, one
OL,12,Fthat involves the people of Penarth
OL,13,Fwho were after all the ones affected
OL,14,Fby this decision.
OL,16,F"That should be a pre-requisition for
OL,17,Fany decision of this magnitude and not
OL,18,Fsomething to be disregarded as has
OL,19,Fhappened in this case.
