OL,7,F"Penarthians have a right to be heard
OL,8,Fbut it seems that the Vale council
OL,9,Fdoesn't agree.
OL,11,F"Now we have emails obtained by FOI by
OL,12,Fthe Save Cosmeston group that seem to
OL,13,Fsuggest a council officer wanted to
OL,14,F'avoid any sort of publicity about the
OL,15,Fplan' and that a 15-year term for the
OL,16,Faqua park was on the table and that
OL,17,Fwas in January this year.
OL,19,F"That's quite concerning and I think
OL,20,Fwe need clarity from the leader or the
OL,21,Fcabinet about this specific issue."
