OL,7,FAn email from a Vale Council officer
OL,8,Fto Aqua Park Group on January 23,
OL,9,F2025, said there was an agreement in
OL,10,Fplace for the council to pursue a
OL,11,Flicence for the company to trial an
OL,12,Fattraction at Cosmeston Lakes this
OL,13,Fsummer.
OL,15,FIt goes on to add that a report on the
OL,16,Fproposal will need to go before
OL,17,Fcouncil cabinet members and states "it
OL,18,Fwill be essential to avoid any sort of
OL,19,Fpublicity about your move before the
OL,20,Fcabinet report is agreed".
