OL,7,FAn email sent to the council by Aqua
OL,8,FPark Group on January 27 lists a
OL,9,Fnumber of "notes for discussion" ahead
OL,10,Fof a meeting between them and officers.
OL,12,FAmong these are proposals to discuss
OL,13,Fpayment, additional revenue that can
OL,14,Fbe expected, pre-negotiation on a
OL,15,Fpotential 15-year term, and other
OL,16,Fpotential activities like
OL,17,Fpaddleboarding, open water swimming,
OL,18,Fand pedalo hire.
