OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,F"No agreement to begin a trial was
OL,8,Fmade prior to cabinet's decision and
OL,9,Fwe did not enter into any commercial
OL,10,Farrangement with the operator until
OL,11,FNatural Resources Wales gave its
OL,12,Fassent in May. Decisions of this
OL,13,Fnature can only be taken by the
OL,14,Fcouncil's cabinet. They do, however,
OL,15,Fneed preparatory work to be done by
OL,16,Fcouncil staff.
