OL,7,F"Again this is normal practice for
OL,8,Fdrafting a heads of terms document for
OL,9,Fconsideration before any cabinet
OL,10,Fapproval. During any such preliminary
OL,11,Fdiscussions we may sometimes advise
OL,12,Fpotential partners not to share any
OL,13,Fdetails of proposals in advance of
OL,14,Fthese being subject to formal
OL,15,Fdemocratic scrutiny and the final
OL,16,Fdecision of cabinet.
