OL,7,F"In this instance it would not have
OL,8,Fbeen appropriate for the potential
OL,9,Foperator to announce the aqua park was
OL,10,Fdue to open as no decision had yet
OL,11,Fbeen made by cabinet. The council has
OL,12,Fat no point tried to prevent scrutiny
OL,13,Fof its decision to trial the use of
OL,14,FCosmeston lakes for commercial
OL,15,Factivities.
