OL,7,F"At each step of the process decisions
OL,8,Fhave been taken in line with the
OL,9,Fcouncil's governance structures. These
OL,10,Fdecisions have been clearly documented
OL,11,Fand are in the public domain.
OL,12,FRecordings of every cabinet, scrutiny
OL,13,Fcommittee, and council meeting where
OL,14,Fthis issue has been discussed can be
